ild narrative hierarchies on-the-fly, adapting to genre, tone, and character dynamics without rigid templates. This significantly improves generalization over HRG’s reliance on predefined plot structures like the hero’s journey. The result is a system that is not only efficient but also cognitively plausible, enabling emergent storytelling behaviors while maintaining interpretability through traceable concept activations.

